A delegation of Ogoni leaders, led by HRM King G.N.K. Gininwa (JP) OFR, Gbenemene Tai Kingdom on Friday, August 12, paid a courtesy visit to President Muhammadu Buhari at the Aso Rock presidential villa in Abuja.

Former Super Eagles captain, Joseph Yobo was also a part of the delegation that visited the president this morning.

